    ValueWithAttributes Certification

      • http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/profile/v0:Certification

      • Description

        Information about certifications or accreditation held by the company.
        Additional Documentation 
        Type Value
        Implementers Assigned XSD Type: {http://chameleon.anonymous/ns}FreeTextType
